Rick: Alive, Lori: Rick's wife. Also alive, but also having sex with Rick's best friend. Carl: Rick's son. Alive Shane: Rick's best friend, currently having sex with his wife though. Not to friendly. Glenn: Member of the group Rick now leads. Alive. Dale: Alive. Convinces Andrea to keep living once her sister dies. Andrea: Begrudgingly alive. Wanted to die after her sister did. Dale convinced her otherwise. Amy: Andrea's sister, dead. Daryl: Merle's brother. Alive, and very unhappy about his brothers predicament. Merle: Handless, but impressively alive. Author's note: Many other characters are in season 1, however overall significance to the story is not really established until later seasons. 
